00:30:17.732 --> 00:30:24.105 line:90% position:50% align:center
And now this time it’s you,
But there’s something you can do:

00:30:24.105 --> 00:30:33.014 line:90% position:50% align:center
Learn from the experience,
And take the help our loving God provides.

00:30:33.014 --> 00:30:39.521 line:90% position:50% align:center
Get back up when you’re down.
You can turn this around.

00:30:39.521 --> 00:30:45.760 line:90% position:50% align:center
Get back up; stand up tall.
You can learn from a fall.

00:30:45.760 --> 00:30:49.030 line:90% position:50% align:center
Just reach out;
take his hand.

00:30:49.030 --> 00:30:52.667 line:90% position:50% align:center
He’ll raise you up—
make you stand.

00:30:52.667 --> 00:31:00.742 line:90% position:50% align:center
And one thing that’s for sure:
You’ll be stronger than before

00:31:00.742 --> 00:31:05.613 line:90% position:50% align:center
If you learn from a fall.

00:31:15.757 --> 00:31:21.796 line:90% position:50% align:center
Another dawn is breaking,
And your heart may be aching.

00:31:21.796 --> 00:31:28.469 line:90% position:50% align:center
But you can’t go back in time.
You have to see it through.

00:31:28.469 --> 00:31:34.642 line:90% position:50% align:center
